    <!-- Section A: Specialize -->
    <section id="home-a" class="text-center py-2">
        <div class="container">
           <h2 class="section-title">I Specilize In</h2> 
           <div class="bottom-line"></div>
           <p>Website designs and development, Web applications 
               client side and server side applications development</p>
               <div class="specials">
                   <div>
                       <i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-2x"></i>
                       <h3>Concepting</h3>
                    <p>Ordinary ideas and general thoughts that occur in the mind,
                        skills and knowledge, alongside my client persona are well represented in designs.
                        These are fundamental building blocks of the concept.</p>
                   </div>
                <div>
                    <i class="fas fa-desktop fa-2x"></i>
                    <h3>Web Interface Designs</h3>
                    <p>I design websites that are fully displayed on the internet.
                        I pay lots of attentions to the user experience aspects of website development rather than software development.
                        My two most common methods for designing websites are, responsive websites and adaptive design.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <i class="fas fa-object-group fa-2x"></i>
                    <h3>Frontend And Backend Development</h3>
                    <p>I write the codes which focuses on the visual elements of a website or app that a user will interact with (the client
                        side).
                        As well as the Back-end Developping which works on the server-side development.
                        With the focus on databases, scripting, and website architecture</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up fa-2x"></i>
                    <h3>Interaction</h3>
                    <p>I focus also on creating engaging interfaces with well thought out behaviors.
                        With good understanding, I can anticipate how my client might interact with the system,
                        I fix problems early, as well as invent new ways of doing things</p>
                </div>
               </div>
        </div>
