        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">
                My Creative Process
            </h2>
            <div class="bottom-line"></div>
            <p class="lead">All of my Web Interface Designs are user
                friendly and user exprience to represent the client's story</p>
                 <div class="process">
                     <div>
                         <i class="fas fa-file-alt fa-4x process-icon my-2">
                             <div class="process-step">1</div>
                         </i>
                         <h3>Discuss The Project</h3>
                        <p>Before starting any project, I capture the project story or expose if you like.
                            I use project management software to execute it stage by stage with Agile Methodology</p>
                     </div>
                    <div>
                        <i class="fas fa-desktop fa-4x process-icon my-2">
                            <div class="process-step">2</div>
                        </i>
                        <h3>Brainstorming ^ Concept</h3>
                        <p>Brainstorming is the way, I try to come up with ideas or solutions to a problem, either on my own or in a
                            group. ... researching..</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <i class="fas fa-object-group fa-4x process-icon my-2">
                            <div class="process-step">3</div>
                        </i>
                        <h3>Web Interface Planning</h3>
                        <p>I design for Web applications that interact with my clients.
                            By good planning and data resources, my clients can read the content of my web application and also manipulate the
                            data.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <i class="fas fa-thumbs-up fa-4x process-icon my-2">
                            <div class="process-step">4</div>
                        </i>
                        <h3>Interaction</h3>
                        <p>I make the difference clear between static content and web application.
                            Client can only read the content of website but not manipulate the data</p>
                    </div>
                 </div>
        </div>
    </section>

